Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.73,0:00:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這片寂靜撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.30,0:00:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領整個世界\N來到熾熱之焰的最深處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.56,0:00:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灌注在朝天高舉的憤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.63,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度點燃你的熱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.80,0:00:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸騰不已的火紅熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.04,0:00:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都已無法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.48,0:00:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一片黑暗的明天\N燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.89,0:01:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍衛弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.42,0:01:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.86,0:01:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無畏懼的向前奔馳吧\N直到衝過那深紅色的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.91,0:01:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一刻燃盡一切吧\N超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.62,0:01:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切都已經...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.46,0:01:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落入我的手中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來就只剩下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.10,0:01:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實捏碎而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.11,0:01:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.81,0:01:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在城內所有地方\N都沒有看到斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.76,0:02:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,膽敢反抗我們的人類啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.72,0:02:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好好去體會一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.79,0:02:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,體會自己有多愚蠢\N了解自己只是不完全的生命體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.07,0:02:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.41,0:03:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於那些因痛苦而迷惘的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.64,0:03:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就賜予他們\N聚集時所能得到的領導與安全感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.88,0:03:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且再給予其行動目的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「在重力衰弱的時刻」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.39,0:03:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要找到斗牙少爺喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然放心交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定一定喔\N我們說好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定一定!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保證...是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.69,0:03:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我嗎?\N是我把他逼成這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是金鋼飛拳\N還有必殺劍才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好帥氣啊感覺好強啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可說是把男人的夢想與浪漫\N全都集結於一身呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這台超重神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂不懂啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.27,0:04:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把諸多武器型兵器\N全部都裝備上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.58,0:04:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了會增加重量之外\N其他可是一點好處也沒有喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.15,0:04:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.18,0:04:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神與各武裝分開搭載的\N超重騎警比較起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.85,0:04:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機體的總合性能差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道你在放什麼屁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.59,0:04:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不過就是EFA的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有駕駛一機\N搭載一種武裝的本事而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這該不會是...點心吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯是"燒賣龍"的中華肉包喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.77,0:04:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太感謝妳了裘依露\N我肚子正餓呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很了不起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要再等個3天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.22,0:04:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神.神機超重神\N就能徹底復活啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.29,0:05:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐的事...有沒有消息呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.64,0:05:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為被爆風炸飛的重鑽機\N艙蓋是完全打開的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.88,0:05:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可能就這麼捲入爆炸之中了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不可能的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.78,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她可是琉菜小姐耶\N一定早就逃離了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我停止!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哭喔...裘依露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.54,0:05:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定了\N在修好超重神之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕對不會哭的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.44,0:05:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果掉眼淚的話\N痛苦也會這麼流掉的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.19,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不想藉著哭泣\N來讓自己逃離這次悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.89,0:06:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定了我絕對不哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.60,0:06:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要背負著所有悲傷\N全力做好我現在能做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.07,0:06:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣一直奮戰下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.24,0:06:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.51,0:06:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信大家一定都沒事的是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在還不可以認輸對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.99,0:06:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了今晚也要來拼個通宵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.29,0:06:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家會把你們\N整修的閃閃動人、又光又亮的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要問問題的是我才對吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜的重鑽機呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.67,0:06:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.71,0:06:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.91,0:06:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊...\N妳到底要我說幾遍才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.35,0:07:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好歹也是傷患耶\N乖乖的回去床上躺著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們救了我我很感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就算如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.55,0:07:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不表示EFA就有權力\N可以這樣拘禁我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.59,0:07:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等妳體內的G因子資料\N測量結束之後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.63,0:07:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我失去意識的時候\N妳們有對我隨便亂來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要做這種蠢事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.24,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人看不下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.84,0:07:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連身為士兵最基本的\N自我控制都做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便表達自己情緒的情形\N也太過頭了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城琉菜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.42,0:07:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我們徹底不同類型的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.76,0:07:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼時候\N都只會想著同伴的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.06,0:07:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很直率的就把情緒表達出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.27,0:07:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是連一點戰士的自覺\N或尊嚴都沒有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能把斗牙交給這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要駕駛超重神呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我就不可以呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.68,0:08:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了各位\N我會報答你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准說這麼見外的話哦英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.25,0:08:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為斗牙已經是\N我們重要的朋友之一啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.89,0:08:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.09,0:08:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那雖然很趕但我們馬上...\N先等一下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了怎麼現在還這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快關機啦高須
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電視現在正在播出\N上次救了超重神的那些機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼! 真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.07,0:09:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當超重神衝擊性的敗北時\N以壓倒性的戰鬥力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.14,0:09:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擊退外星異種的EFA新機動模組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.85,0:09:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經從專家口中\N傳出證實存在的消息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.45,0:09:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於量產型超重神.超重騎警\N政府將於本日正午
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.39,0:09:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於航行中的航空母艦\N多倫多號上進行的總統演說中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式對外發表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.70,0:09:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於在我們眼前出現的超重騎警...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.10,0:09:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀白色的機體內\N到底隱藏著怎麼樣的性能呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.27,0:09:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就是把超重神"亮"產\N然後去打倒外星異種嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下子就真的能安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.46,0:10:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要快點回到戰線上哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.40,0:10:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護地球的和平吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個訊號...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.81,0:10:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(本日關東地區天氣晴朗)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(但因位置不同)\N(有些地點會有雷雨出現...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.08,0:10:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種現在正朝著北太平洋\N多倫多空母方向直行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我聽好囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.70,0:10:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次作戰不但是你們的出道戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.27,0:10:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時更是賭上我們人類未來\N以及一切未來的一戰喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊凡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.55,0:10:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次作戰是不許失敗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.52,0:10:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡全力去摧毀敵人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.99,0:11:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不說我也是這麼打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.85,0:11:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是打從心底歡迎你的來訪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.55,0:11:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下降中的外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.83,0:11:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將在186秒後\N與多倫多號航空母艦接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.67,0:11:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有找到斗牙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.07,0:11:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.50,0:11:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才就一直通知...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.34,0:11:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻一點反應都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種急速接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經進入目視距離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.39,0:12:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還在甲板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行快帶他去避難!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.39,0:12:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.49,0:12:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種要與本艦衝撞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.36,0:12:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.20,0:12:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統所搭乘的空母被...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.00,0:12:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電波干擾情形太嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空母的情形、外星異種的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.04,0:12:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都還無法進行確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.04,0:12:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等能夠確認的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.78,0:12:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再立刻通知我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統被...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經被打死了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議的畫面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由超重騎警所發出的工學力場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經將外星異種困住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是新兵器的能力之一嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.31,0:13:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰將的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.62,0:13:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員出擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星辰群光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.13,0:13:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就好好教教你\N誰才是這片天空中的女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.44,0:13:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們EFA引以為傲的\N地球新生守護天使們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.17,0:13:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"超重騎警"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.84,0:13:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始與外星異種作戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.21,0:13:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們雖然在前次戰役中\N失去了偉大的英雄"超重神"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.22,0:13:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼之英雄的魂魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在此時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.96,0:13:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又取得新的軀體而轉生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.56,0:13:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去! 隨便鬼扯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.79,0:13:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣\N那我就開超重皇去解決牠們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.33,0:13:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.83,0:14:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對鋼鐵惡魔處以天譴的\N鋼鐵天使們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他們的英姿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.21,0:14:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力放射標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由重力發電機所產生的\N重力子力場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.36,0:14:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當與裝甲或武裝構造結合的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重騎警...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.57,0:14:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會成為凌駕各式兵器的超兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德...曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.49,0:14:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥他來殺我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.82,0:14:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.09,0:14:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你振作點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.20,0:15:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在展開工學力場的那一瞬間\N會出現空檔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.14,0:15:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道超重皇這個弱點的\N只有我和...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.94,0:15:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到那個人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他居然還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都沒指望了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有指望了...一切都沒救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法為過去犯下的錯贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.49,0:15:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼躲進黑暗之中\N又對未來感到恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.59,0:15:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點出息也沒有的男人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.60,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誤把自己的美學當作真實的小丑...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.60,0:15:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個愚蠢的男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.38,0:15:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都走到現在了你還想要逃避嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.42,0:16:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了東西囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.03,0:16:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅者之鑽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.17,0:16:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.54,0:16:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不是為了這副德性的你\N才繼承這張假面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.47,0:16:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.67,0:16:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是為了什麼\N才這樣一直努力奮戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.38,0:16:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了地球...\N為了讓妳們居住的這顆星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.45,0:16:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要走上和我的星球相同的命運...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.49,0:16:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了地球為了我們...\N雖然的確是這樣子沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是並不只是這樣吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭是由你引起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.23,0:16:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該也要由你\N自己來親手做個了斷才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己的...戰爭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就繼續縮在那邊發抖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.85,0:17:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要踏上我所選擇的戰場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力強襲飛彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.03,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來交給我吧伊凡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開球囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重隕石射門!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.45,0:17:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們幾個居然都這麼威風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.22,0:17:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好! 那我就來負責最後的壓軸\N解決掉那個大頭目吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.36,0:17:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好猛啊!\N果然夠資格當我的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太適合當謝幕用的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.67,0:17:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我這一擊不就能拯救地球了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要來囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.01,0:18:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上送你一記必殺的超重光束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.65,0:18:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.82,0:18:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重光束居然毫無效果!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我不對...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不論面前\N到底有怎麼樣的命運在等著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.90,0:18:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都絕不該逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.78,0:18:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.88,0:18:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到我們的戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.82,0:19:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.28,0:19:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎讓各位掛心了\N還請各位見諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.76,0:19:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎您回來指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.63,0:19:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...現在狀況如何了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時機已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.30,0:19:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此刻隨著這份光輝\N我們人類...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的地球!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.37,0:19:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都將自外星異種的魔爪中\N獲得解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.77,0:19:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行! 那東西不可以破壞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.35,0:19:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電光雷霆...轟炸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那道光...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥你終於想用那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來對付地球了是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.34,0:20:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個"轟炸"是從哪蹦出來的呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,JACKOFF(回家吃自己吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.95,0:20:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敝人將與全人類一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.55,0:20:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將超重騎警的勝利\N視為我們的榮耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭已經進入最後階段了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.32,0:20:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將會把外星異種\N徹底的逐出地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.26,0:20:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敝人堅信超重騎警有能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.96,0:20:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迅速達成此一任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個騙人的死老頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.67,0:20:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底...做了什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.54,0:20:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是人類...不\N這是所有地球人的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.11,0:20:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重騎警將在正義之名下\N為人類帶來決定性的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許現在就是需要的時候了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.49,0:21:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要能夠\N一掃這片陰霾的太陽光輝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.73,0:21:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.76,0:21:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在是不是應該要\N迎接即將返航的鋼鐵天使們呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你們喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人渣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.50,0:21:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別來弄髒我們這條街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.57,0:21:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這死小鬼\N別只是給你好臉色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.58,0:21:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就開始得寸進尺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄髒這條街的是你們才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.16,0:21:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這丫頭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.47,0:21:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的一點都沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.67,0:21:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全和以前的你一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.31,0:22:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因熱戀而無法成眠的夜晚\N已經看膩了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.89,0:22:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要聽到人的聲音\N所以隨意打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.96,0:22:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了靠不住的語音留言\N你現在到底在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.77,0:22:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映著冰箱內的燈光\N我在狹小的宇宙裡彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.78,0:22:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的唱片\N唱針已經跳開不知幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.05,0:22:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信這不變的溫度\N一直到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.23,0:22:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.00,0:22:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們手牽著手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.67,0:23:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N淺淺呼吸籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.21,0:23:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.69,0:23:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們閉上雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.52,0:23:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜進你夢裡的\N甜美節奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.57,0:23:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.20,0:23:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有愛娜呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.71,0:23:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都還平安嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.11,0:23:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不能把斗牙\N交給你們這種玩票性質的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.58,0:23:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼?\N這話是什麼意思!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.45,0:23:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我姓飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.65,0:23:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比任何人都還要了解斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.12,0:23:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙就由我們超重騎警接收了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.09,0:23:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.92,0:23:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點幫幫斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.72,0:23:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回「紅之牙」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.96,0:23:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙你已經是我的人了